import React from 'react'
import { BrowserRouter as Router, Route, Link } from 'react-router-dom'
import AppBar from '@material-ui/core/AppBar'
import MenuItem from '@material-ui/core/MenuItem'
import Menu from '@material-ui/core/Menu'
const styles = {
  appBar: {
    display: 'flex',
    flexDirection: 'row',
    padding: 15,
    backgroundColor: '#343a40'
  },
  linkText: { color: 'white', marginRight: 15, textDecoration: 'none' }
}

export default (props) => {
  return (
    <header>
      <AppBar style={styles.appBar}>
        <Link style={styles.linkText} to="/">
          Ryan Blakeman
        </Link>
        <Link style={styles.linkText} to="/">
          Home
        </Link>
        <Link style={styles.linkText} to="/software/">
          Software
        </Link>
        <Link style={styles.linkText} to="/games/">
          Games
        </Link>
        <Link style={styles.linkText} to="/research/">
          Research
        </Link>
        <Link style={styles.linkText} to="/resume/">
          Resume
        </Link>
      </AppBar>
    </header>
  )
}
